column5: I waiting up for the CCmt report I need to see some fish before sleep tonight as I didn't catch anything myself today.
Although I did catch some fish today, their report would make my dreams sweeter.
Give me 10 minutes...hands are still shaking...downloading pics from the camera....
all right I fell like Xmas eve
Hurry up i gotta go to bed.
Cliff, I am starting to charge you the late fee now..... and will send you my sleeping pill bill...
